author: castagna
msg: JENA-36 - Renamed log4j.properties to jena-log4j.properties and made all the Jena cmd line tools use that via System.setProperty("log4j.configuration", "jena-log4j.properties"). Including a log4j.properties file in a jar which is supposed to be used as a library is not a good practice and can cause troubles to people.
